Title: Wrong age reported for ESX snapshots
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Component: checks
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Edition: cre
State: unknown
Version: 1.6.0p14
Date: 1594104291

When calculating age of snapshots timezone was not taken into account. With
this fix a time_reference will be stored together with the snapshot timestamps
to be able to calculate a correct and accurate snapshot age
